{
  "id": "5bbd7552d337770013c40d10",
  "title": "機械に速読を教える",
  "created": 1539143000,
  "updated": 1647494506,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5bbd7552d337770013c40d10",
      "text": "機械に速読を教える",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143000,
      "updated": 1539143000
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7558aff09e0000771a81",
      "text": "\t機械のインプット速度は人間より桁違いに速い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143000,
      "updated": 1539143015
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7566aff09e0000771a84",
      "text": " なので機械に[速読]を教える必要性があるなんて思いもよらない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143015,
      "updated": 1539143219
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7596aff09e0000771a85",
      "text": " だがしかし[修辞的残像]の考え方からすると、理解には適切な速度があり、ゆっくり読みすぎると理解の妨げになる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143063,
      "updated": 1539143117
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd75ccaff09e0000771a86",
      "text": " 機械の読書は人間と比べて圧倒的に速いが、一字一句追っていく「遅い読み方」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143117,
      "updated": 1539143139
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd75ebaff09e0000771a87",
      "text": " もっと速い読み方をするべきなのではないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143148,
      "updated": 1539143154
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd75f2aff09e0000771a88",
      "text": " つまり機械に速読を教えるべきなのではないか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143154,
      "updated": 1539143159
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd769baff09e0000771a89",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143324,
      "updated": 1539143324
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd755baff09e0000771a82",
      "text": "\t目次を読む",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143004,
      "updated": 1539143331
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76a3aff09e0000771a8b",
      "text": " \t目次が構造化されたデータとして入っている電子書籍は楽",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143331,
      "updated": 1539143341
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76acaff09e0000771a8c",
      "text": "  そうでない場合、紙面のテキストデータから目次のツリー構造を把握する必要がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143341,
      "updated": 1539143373
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76ccaff09e0000771a8d",
      "text": " \t作られたツリー構造がアウトプット",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143373,
      "updated": 1539143402
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76e9aff09e0000771a8e",
      "text": " キーワード探し",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143402,
      "updated": 1539143409
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76f1aff09e0000771a8f",
      "text": " \t既存のキーワード抽出プログラムでできる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143409,
      "updated": 1539143417
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7706aff09e0000771a91",
      "text": "  「ざっと眺めて目に飛び込んでくる」は何か",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143430,
      "updated": 1539143453
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd76f9aff09e0000771a90",
      "text": "  \t一行分のテキストが入力されて、そこからキーワード抽出",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143417,
      "updated": 1539143459
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7723aff09e0000771a92",
      "text": "   繰り返し出てくるキーワードがプライミングによって認知効率が上がり、目に飛び込む",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143459,
      "updated": 1539143477
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd772daff09e0000771a93",
      "text": " 質問を作る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143470,
      "updated": 1539143526
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7765aff09e0000771a94",
      "text": " \tこれは結構高度だなぁ、どうやって作るのか",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143526,
      "updated": 1539143537
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd77b6aff09e0000771a98",
      "text": "  「<キーフレーズX>とは何か？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143607,
      "updated": 1539143620
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd77c4aff09e0000771a99",
      "text": "  「<キーフレーズX>と<キーフレーズY>の関係は？」",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143620,
      "updated": 1539143635
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7770aff09e0000771a96",
      "text": " マインドマップを作る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143537,
      "updated": 1539143541
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7775aff09e0000771a97",
      "text": " \t[連想ネットワーク]をツリー構造で出力",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143541,
      "updated": 1647494506
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7844aff09e0000771a9a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143748,
      "updated": 1539143748
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd769daff09e0000771a8a",
      "text": "[機械が自由にScrapboxに書き込みができるとしたら本を読んで何を書くのか]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143326,
      "updated": 1539143752
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7848aff09e0000771a9c",
      "text": "\tその本の目次",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143753,
      "updated": 1539143757
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd784caff09e0000771a9d",
      "text": " その本のキーワード",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143757,
      "updated": 1539143762
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7852aff09e0000771a9e",
      "text": " その本を読んで持った問いとその答え",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143762,
      "updated": 1539143767
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7857aff09e0000771a9f",
      "text": " その本の内容に関する連想ネットワークをツリー状にしたもの",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143767,
      "updated": 1539143780
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7864aff09e0000771aa0",
      "text": " \t箇条書きでかける",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143780,
      "updated": 1539143784
    },
    {
      "id": "5bbd7844aff09e0000771a9b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1539143749,
      "updated": 1539143749
    }
  ]
}